# ─── EmailJS — Email Delivery for Contact & Investor Forms ───────────────────
#
# Setup steps:
#   1. Create a free account at https://www.emailjs.com/
#   2. Add an Email Service (Gmail / Outlook / SMTP) → copy the Service ID
#
#   3. Create Template: Contact Form Notification  (VITE_EJS_CONTACT_TEMPLATE)
#      - Sends to: contact@drivtech.in
#      - Subject: "New Inquiry — {{inquiry_type}} from {{from_name}}"
#      - Variables: from_name, from_email, phone, inquiry_type, message
#
#   4. Create Template: Investor Autoresponder     (VITE_EJS_TEMPLATE_ID)
#      - Sends to: {{to_email}}  (the investor's own email)
#      - Subject: "Your DRIV Investor Brochure"
#      - Variables: from_name, from_email, phone, invest_range, city, message
#
#   5. Create Template: Investor Team Notification (VITE_EJS_NOTIFY_ID)
#      - Sends to: contact@drivtech.in
#      - Subject: "New Investor Interest — {{invest_range}}"
#      - Variables: from_name, from_email, phone, invest_range, city, message
#
#   6. Get your Public Key from Account → API Keys
#   7. Copy this file to .env and fill in the values below
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Sheets — paste the Apps Script Web App URL here after deploying
VITE_SHEETS_WEBHOOK_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/YOUR_DEPLOYMENT_ID/exec

VITE_EJS_SERVICE_ID=service_xxxxxxx
VITE_EJS_PUBLIC_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Contact page form
VITE_EJS_CONTACT_TEMPLATE=template_xxxxxxx

# Investor page form
VITE_EJS_TEMPLATE_ID=template_xxxxxxx
VITE_EJS_NOTIFY_ID=template_xxxxxxx
